      "content": "<ul><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">This feature applies for POS orders &amp; QR Order and Pay orders only, not Beep Delivery orders.</span></li></ul><p></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Changing table numbers can only be done for Open orders or before payment is made.</span></li></ul>",
