      "step_order": 2,
      "step_title": "Change table via Table Layout",
      "content": "<p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">1. Go to your table layout page to view all tables occupied</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">2. Tap on the 3 dot menu in the top right corner to choose Move Order.</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">3. Select a table that you want to change; after choosing the tables, they turn Red</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">4. Choose a table that your customer wishes to move to; you can select one of the tables selected or an empty table.</span></p>",
